text: Nischal or Nischol is a surname of Indian origin. It is also a given name used in India and Nepal. == Surname == * Dega Nischal, Indian cricketer * Paul Nischal, a politician from the United Kingdom * Navin Nischol, Indian actor * Praveen Nischol, Indian producer, director and writer ==Given name== * Nischal Basnet, a Nepalese film personality Category:Indian family names Category:Punjabi tribes
title: Nischal
